@startuml
state EnterPin as "Enter PIN"
state VerifyPin as "Verify Entered PIN"
state OptionsAvailable as "Options Available"
state WithdrawalApproved as "Withdrawal Approved"
state CashDispensed as "Cash Dispensed"
state ReceiptPrinted as "Receipt Printed"
state CardReturned as "Card Returned"
state ResetSystem as "Reset System"

EnterPin --> VerifyPin: PIN entered
VerifyPin --> OptionsAvailable: PIN verified
OptionsAvailable --> WithdrawalApproved: User approves withdrawal
WithdrawalApproved --> CashDispensed: Cash dispensed
CashDispensed --> ReceiptPrinted: Receipt printed
ReceiptPrinted --> CardReturned: Card returned
CardReturned --> ResetSystem: System resets
ResetSystem --> [*]: Ready for next user
@enduml
